data.text: Forced - After you fail a skill test while investigating this location: Discard an asset you control.
{Nature/power-lightning} If there are no clues here: Draw 1 supply crate cards. (Group limit once per game at this location).

Forced - After you fail a skill test at this location: This location takes 1 damage. If the location reaches zero health, all players and ships docked at this location take 5 damage. {Nature/power-lightning} If there are no clues here: Draw 1 supply crate cards. (Group limit once per game at this location).
Forced - After you fail a skill test while investigating this location: Take 1 shield damage.
Forced - After you reveal location: Search the encounter deck and discard pile for an enemy and put it into play engaged with you (2 copies instead if there are 3 or 4 investigators in the game).

Forced - After you reveal location: Search the encounter deck for a Parasite enemy and spawn it on your ship (2 copies instead if there are 3 or 4 investigators in the game). Shuffle the encounter deck.
{Nature/power-lightning} If there are no clues here: Draw 1 supply crate cards. (Group limit once per game at this location).
Forced - After you perform a move action during which you move from this location: Take 2 hull damage.
{Weapons/bottom-right-3d-arrow} Heal 3 damage from one player. (Limit once per round.)
